Dialogs.Dialog: It's just a rumor, but I heard there are some really good donut shops.
Ah！ Do you mean the fabled Donut Wagon？
I've heard about those rumors too. It's like finding a god of death, but it's very delicious.
A god of death, huh... Well, I want to look for the shop and try them.
Then, if you find it, please let me know, okay？
Of course！ I enjoy eating together.
(Ah, isn't that the fabled Donut Shop？)
(Okay, I'll get one for you ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Wow！ By any chance, is this a donut from the rumored shop？
Yes, that's right. We should eat now.
Mmm... it's so delicious！ It's my first time eating a donut like this.
It's true... It's my first too.
It's a wagon donut shop... so cute♪ I wonder if I'll open a store someday. Hehe.
You opening a shop, huh？ That store will surely become popular, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hey, do you like crepes, ▲主人公＊▲？
I guess... Why？ You want me to make some for you？
No. The other day, Mama bought me a crepe from a store outside...
They were so rich and I wanted you to try them again. But, it wasn't there because it was a mobile shop.
I see... So, if you want to eat, you have to find it by chance, right？
Looks like it. Mama has never seen it since.
I see. So why don't we try to find it together？
Really？ I'd be happy if we find it♪
(Ah, is that the rumored crepe shop？)
Look at that store over there.
The crepe shop！ Wow, you really found it♪
My intuition works wonders, I guess.
Yeah, and they smell good too. Hey, do you want to get one？
I know I said I wanted you to try them... but I really wanted to eat them myself.
Yes, I wonder if we can do something about it.
If you eat a sweet and cold gelato, you'll feel refreshed, won't you？
You know, a friend from my class told me they found a delicious gelato shop♪
But it's a mobile shop, so it doesn't mean that you can always buy it.
I wonder if it's a seasonal shop... All right, let's go find it.
(Oh, is that the rumored gelato shop？)
See？ The shop's over there ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
What do you think about my finding？
Hehe, it's amazing. Thank you for your hard work under the heat♪
It's because I wanted you to try them too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Thank you. Do you want to eat one together？
Mmmm, it's cold and delicious！ I feel refreshed.
What kind of smell is it？
Smells like sweet chestnuts♪ I'm kidding.
This season, a mobile sweet chestnut shop appears in the city. I'm looking forward to eat them every year.
Oh, then I want to try them too.
(Ah, is that the sweet chestnut shop？)
(Okay, I should buy some for ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Doesn't it smell like autumn already, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Huh？... Ah, that！ The smell of autumn.
Actually, I bought some chestnuts for you.
Sweet chestnuts！ Did you remember what I told you back then？
Your plan for a fun autumn has been achieved this year ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Hehe, if you're looking forward to it, there's still more, you know？
Does it make that happy, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
You just have to think about the funny things in winter.
Fun things in winter... for example？
For example, at the baked potato shop, you can buy and eat hot and sweet potatoes.
I see, you like baked sweet potatoes after all.
I love them♪ Especially the ones from a shop that opens this season, but I can't find it.
I see, don't worry about that.
(Ah, is that the baked sweet potato shop？)
What's wrong？ Sounds like you're having fun.
I found something fun in winter, look...
Ah, a sweet potato♪ Is it from that baked sweet potato shop？
Yes. I remembered what you told me, and I found it, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
It's still hot. Can I eat it？
(You look so happy eating sweet potatoes, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
People around town has been talking about the same topic.
Ah, is it the story about seeing an UFO？
That's right！ Did you hear about it too ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yes, that's the only topic I heard around lately.
I see. Now, I think Towano is getting excited with the UFO sightings.
Say, some people were watching at the same time, right？ I wonder why no one took a picture.
If you witness the UFO, don't forget to take a picture, okay？
Take a look at this, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Ah！ This is... it's the UFO... isn't it？
Amazing... it's real... I wanted to see it.
If you show this to everyone, it will cause a fuss.
Maybe so, I was lucky anyway.
Hey, do you know about Towassy？
Yes, a rare beast that seems to live in Lake Towano.
Huh, is there such a rumor？
This seems to be a famous story from olden days.
When it comes to being in the local area, it seems to be interesting.
That's right. True or not. It's fun to be excited like this.
(If I find it, I wonder if I can take a picture.)
I'll show you something good, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Take a look. Do you know what is in the picture？
It's a genuine photo taken by me.
I was really surprised. No way to discover it by myself.
It's okay, I want to see...
The final test are coming soon.
What's wrong？ You put such a grim face.
It's the tension before the test, it's a good meaning！
Hehe, what's that. By the way, what is your goal？ I want to know.
Hey, the mid-term tests are coming, are you ready？
Hey, the final exam is approaching, are you ready？
It doesn't seem you're doing very well... Are you okay？
That's not true, it's going to be okay.
I see, then what is your goal？
Hey, are you studying properly for mid-terms？
Hey, are you studying properly for the finals？
You can't get good results if you put such a grim face, you know？
Don't worry... I'll be fine for that day.
Really？ Then, I wonder if you could tell me what your goal is.
Really？ Are you okay with such a high goal？
Well, the higher the goal, the more it keeps me motivated.
Eh！？ Now that was a surprise.
You set the bar high... But, I have faith in you.
Yes, I think it's good. I'll support you.
I have to give it my all.
You say that, but... Are you studying？
Yes. I will do my best.
What made you feel so confident？ In that case, there's nothing for Takane- sensei, is it？
Well, I might want to get help from my sensei.
I see. Yes, you'll be fine.
I'll try it at my own pace.
Is that so？ I'm sure you'll be fine.
Thank you. I get motivated when I hear that.
I see, if you want more... No, it's important to set goals, give it your all！
Well then, let's do our best so we can achieve our goals.
If you need my help, I'll lend it to you. Tell me anytime.
Let's ride this out and survive the tests！
Good work. How did it go？
Good work. Hey, how did the test go？
Good work. How was your performance today？
Then, let's do our best for tomorrow's test.
We will have more tests tomorrow, so let's do our best.
Okay, let's do our best tomorrow. Let's go get'em！
It's finally over. Good work this week.
The tests are finally over. Good work during this week.
It's the end of the test period！ Good job during this week♪
The tests results are up now. I wonder what my result is...
I did it, the first place！
No, it's not a dream！ It's amazing... I looked it over again.
I give up. You made a lot of effort.
I'm in... 1st place！？ I can't believe it...
What's wrong？ Your mouth is hanging open.
Look over there！ I got the 1st place, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Hehe, I always believed in you♪
Hooray！ I'm within the first 10th places.
Ah, did you achieve your goal？ Congrats.
Oh, a pose. Does that mean you have achieved your goals？
Alright, I'm within the first 10 places！
Ah... you achieved your goals. Congrats！
I did my best this time.
Good work. I'm happy with your results♪
I'm glad. I'm within the first 100 places.
Ah！ Did you achieve your goals？ Congrats.
At this rate, let's do our best next time.
I'm glad you achieved your goal.
Let's do our best from now on.
Such a relieved face. Good for you.
Congrats. Next time, let's aim higher.
Was I too reckless to aim for the 1st place？
I think it's good to try anything. Next time, give your best！
Too bad... I didn't get 1st place.
Let's do our best next time, right？ I will also help.
Don't feel too sad, okay？ I don't think it's rational to aim for the 1st place.
Yes. Let's get our revenge next time！
You didn't reach your goal, but I think it's good because you did your best.
It was so cool that you worked hard towards your goal.
I didn't make it in the first 10...
Haha, you don't have to worry that much...
Yes... cheer up. Next time, give it your all.
I'm not within the first 10 places...
This result is just a step！ Let's give our best together.
It's okay！ Next time, you'll be within the 100th places.
Guh... I wasn't in the 100th place.
I can't help it, I'm not making enough effort.
Next time, let's do our best to achieve your goal.
Ugh... I didn't manage to enter the first hundred.
That's a shame, you were almost there.
I can't help it, but I'll do my best next time.
Anyway, good work. It was difficult, but you made an effort.
Yes, good work to you too ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
What do you want to do after finishing the tests？
A date, of course！ Let's have fun together.
When the exams are over... I think summer vacation starts soon, right？
Right. Now we can enjoy it more！
And now that our tests are over, it was almost time for winter vacation... Time goes fast, doesn't it？
Yes. And having said that, let's enjoy the last days of the year and New Year's Eve together.
You know, I heard from a friend...
A story called "The ghost of Towano Castle"
I think so. It seems that you can hear something akin to moans at Towano Castle at night.
Well, it's a common story, but I was interested in that kind of thing.
I was a little worried because my friend was so serious.
Well then, we should go now. It may still be early though.
Right now？ Yes, maybe we should go.
I wonder if it's okay to be around here...
It's quite large... Would you like to walk a little？
Umm, didn't you hear something now？
It's just my imagination. I wonder.
Come to think of it, what happened to that story we talked about before.
I'm still a little worried... I don't mind going out with you again.
This is the place we came last time.
Yeah. Do you want to head back？
(It's a silly story, it's better not to be disappointed if you hear nothing.)
Ah... I wonder if you've heard of it.
You know, "The Legend of Dracula's Mansion".
There's a Western-style house in this town, right？ It's a story about that...
It's like there's some kind of ritual in that house every night.
What kind of ritual is it？
I don't know that. Just strange sounds can be heard.
It sounds like you're interested in it ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Looking at it this way, it's a little scary after all...
No, there's still time... I think it's okay.
That's right... But you can't go in on your own.
However, if we wander around here we're going to be seen as strange...
Yes, I heard it... What kind of sound is that？
I knew it, it's the ritual...
I was scared, but I'm still curious...
Would you go with me again？
...I wonder if we can hear it again.
...I can't hear it, maybe it was my imagination.
I felt like I've heard it clearly before...
By the way, I saw on the news...
I didn't see it. Bigfoot is an unidentified animal, right？
I see. It seems that the footprints of the Bigfoot were found in the mountains.
Huh... You can't know if it's the real thing with only the footprints.
...Come to think of it, that's right.
I wonder if that's the case... But, if you do it you'll get a prize.
It's like a fantasy world, and it's a little exciting.
If it was real, it would be interesting...
It's not going to be like fantasy.
The story of "Bigfoot in the mountains".
It seems to have been someone's prank, after all.
It would be scary if it was there, but I wanted it to remain a mystery if possible.
It was surprising that you were so interested, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I mean, it's not likely that such a strange event will happen around you. I expected it.
I see. It was a prank, after all...
Ah... I wonder if you heard this story.
You know, "The Ghost of the Valley"... That story.
A ghost, huh. I've never heard of it. You're talking about a local story？
Yes, it seems to be in the valley of Oku-Towano.
It's like the ghost of a woman who died and left this world full with regret...
Huh, a ghost of a woman...
Yes, that's the way it is. Seems like it's a tragic love legend...
We talked about the "Ghost of the Valley" before.
Did you find any new information since then？
No, nothing. I took it as just a rumor.
Well, actually, this e-mail came to me...
This.. Is this an e-mail from a ghost？
It's probably a prank, but it's amazing.
...Hey, maybe you were trying to surprise me...
If so... What does that mean...？
(I thought about it. Well, it's interesting...)
Hey, we went to the amusement park together last time, right？
To tell you the truth, it seems that I lost something there.
A lace handkerchief. It was my favorite...
I see... Did you check at the park？
You should do it. It may have been found.
Don't you know the "Amusement Park Costume Ghost" story？
Yes. It likes picking up lost items at the amusement park after it closes.
So, recovering an item picked up by the ghost... You will be cursed...
Ah... so you don't want it to be found.
I wonder if we can go in.
Alright. Let's search for it before it's too late.
...I think we've looked around the place...
We can't find it in this big place, and it's getting late.
What are you two doing here. The park's already closed.
Oh, are you looking for a lace handkerchief？ It's over there.
It's fine. No... I was looking around here with my suit 'cause it's a hassle to change clothes. There's no such rumor.
I'm going to get angry sooner or later, so I'm going to change my back. You should head back home.
That's right... I'm glad I didn't get cursed...
Haha, did you really take it seriously？
I'm here, but... I wonder if they'll let us in.
I can't go on my own... Do you want to find a security guard and ask for it？
It doesn't seem to be there... We should go back for today.
Yes... we can't do anything about it.
Well, I don't think the ghost picked up. I'll go ask at the information desk if it's been found.
A lace handkerchief... It's not here. I'm sorry.
No good... We should go back for today.
